'''恩佐·馬里''' （{{lang-it|Enzo Mari}}，{{bd|1932年|12月31日|2020年|10月19日|catIdx=Mari}}）是著名的意大利[[現代主義|現代派]]藝術家和家具設計師，出生於義大利諾瓦拉，並曾在1962年到1956年就讀於米蘭[[布雷拉美術學院|布雷拉美術學院]]。

馬里的創作靈感主要源自[[美術工藝運動|美術工藝運動]]與[[共產主義|共產主義]]。<ref name=NYT-Enzo>{{cite news|last=Rawsthorn|first=Alice|title=Enzo Mari: A rebel with an obsession for form|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/03/style/03iht-design3.1.17414904.html?_r=1|accessdate=2012-06-27|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2008-10-02|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022080508/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/03/style/03iht-design3.1.17414904.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}}</ref>

==生平==

1978年與藝術史學家{{Le|Lea Vergine}}結婚。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Hilburg|first=Jonathan|date=2020-10-20|title=Italian design legend Enzo Mari dies, a day before his wife, Lea Vergine|url=https://www.archpaper.com/2020/10/italian-design-legend-enzo-mari-lea-vergine-die/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204212634/https://www.archpaper.com/2020/10/italian-design-legend-enzo-mari-lea-vergine-die/|archive-date=2020-12-04|access-date=2020-10-22|website=The Architect’s Newspaper|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[2019冠状病毒病意大利疫情|2020年義大利新冠肺炎流行]]期間確診新冠肺炎，並在2020年10月19日去世，享年88歲。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-19|title=Morto Enzo Mari, icona del design italiano e mondiale|url=https://www.agi.it/cultura/news/2020-10-19/morto-enzo-mari-icona-design-italiano-9998611/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019133708/https://www.agi.it/cultura/news/2020-10-19/morto-enzo-mari-icona-design-italiano-9998611/|archive-date=2020-10-19|access-date=2020-10-28|website=AGI|language=it|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的妻子也在一天後死於新冠肺炎。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-20|title=Morta Lea Vergine, la critica d'arte scompare il giorno dopo suo marito Enzo Mari: era ricoverata con lui in ospedale|url=https://milano.repubblica.it/cronaca/2020/10/20/news/lea_vergine_morta_milano_enzo_mari-271182502/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021224351/https://milano.repubblica.it/cronaca/2020/10/20/news/lea_vergine_morta_milano_enzo_mari-271182502/|archive-date=2020-10-21|access-date=2020-10-28|website=la Repubblica|language=it|dead-url=no}}</ref>

